description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 min Full Body Stretch | Daily Routine for Flexibility & Relaxation' from the channel Anna McNulty.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Welcome to your 2022 flexibility challenge! This relaxing 15 minute full body stretching routine will help you get flexible whether you're a beginner, intermediate or advanced. Feel free to implement this stretch into your daily routine for best results.

Do this warm up first: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BSh4zJHVxs0

2022 Workout & Fitness Challenge: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rDxPfQEKBHw
